title: Modern Warrior vs Chelsea Hart TikTok Battle
description:
This week on Fool Coverage, Manny and Laura talk all about self-love, and being kind to yourself. They also deep dive into TikTok's Modern Warrior's, Chelsea and Lance sharing TOO private details about their toxic relationship, Makeup Geek closing it's doors, Britney Spears' jab at her family during her Las Vegas trip, and much more!
